-- Piramal Healthcare to Acquire BioSyntech for C$3.9 Million; Shares Advance
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-06-22T05:03:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/piramal-healthcare-to-acquire-biosyntech-for-c-3-9-million-shares-advance.html

          
          
             Piramal Healthcare Ltd. plans to
acquire assets of BioSyntech, a biotechnology company developing
novel products in regenerative medicine, according to a
statement today on the National Stock Exchange.  
 Piramal shares gained as much as 1.6 percent in Mumbai
trading after the announcement.  
          
          


  


        